name: Experiment Or Die #43
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. Todays layout consists of several different images that all combine to create an obscured texture and is the first of my designs that I was live tweeting exactly how I was making it. If you check out the process nearly none of the base images are recognizable but all add up to the unexpected and unpredictable background and layout that I ended up with and that is the true beauty of this project. Spontaneous creation. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
